---
title: Miso-Glazed Tofu Bowl with Broccolini & Japanese Mayo
description: Enjoy a dinner that's packed with flavour in every bite. From a miso-infused sweet and savoury glaze on tasty Korean tofu to buttery garlic rice and sautéed veggies, this hearty bowl is a medley of flavour, colour and texture.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/miso-glazed-tofu-rice-bowl-0dcc9d8a.jpg
